Description: Offering a wonderful set of luggage from VERA BRADLEY in the retired Java Blue and Brown Paisley pattern in excellent condition. Used twice. Includes three pieces, a Garment Bag, a Duffle Bag and a round Cosmetic case. Colors nice and bright, no wear anywhere - nearly new. The garment bag measures 23" x 46" x 4". It folds in half for easy carrying by the handles. There are 2 zippered pockets on the interior side for shoes, socks, undergarments, and more. The exterior side also has 1 large pocket with a mesh lining. The garment compartment can be opened by 2 full-length zippers and there are ribbons to tie your clothes in place. The Large Duffle Bag is the perfect travel companion to the Garment Bag. It's open construction lets you pack a huge amount of clothing and accessories in an easy-to-carry space. At 22" long and 11" X 11" square, it easily holds all your folded items, shoes, make-up, and toiletries. It features a full-width rust-proof zipper, an outside end pocket for cell phones and other quick access items, and two extra-long wide padded strap handles. Use the Duffle with the Garment Bag or use it alone as a great overnight or weekend bag. It's even Carry-On compliant. The round cosmetic bag measures 4.5" in height by 8" in length. It has a zip compartment inside in the top, a convenient carry handle on the top and lots of room inside. It has several loop pockets to slip in your cosmetics. Altogether a wonderful travel set in Vera Bradley's most popular pattern ever - now very hard to find, especially in this wonderful condition. From a smoke and pet free home - clean and ready to use.
